Turn left, go to the microwave.
Take the egg out of the microwave.
Turn left, move around the center island to the left, go to the sink on the left.
Wash the egg in the sink with water.
Bring the washed egg back around the center island, to the microwave in the corner to the right.
Put the washed egg in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed egg in the microwave.
